      "The approval gate is universal: any tool that drafts, summarises, translates, transcribes, predicts or decides — commercial platforms, embedded features in existing systems (the care-records vendor's new 'AI summaries' toggle counts), and free public tools — is assessed before use for data protection (where data goes, retention, training use, processor status), clinical safety (error modes, the stakes of its mistakes), and fit (what it is approved FOR, stated narrowly)",
